<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3670837>
    dc:description "FIGURES 257–262. Figs 257–260: Neotanypeza claripennis Schiner (Tanypezidae), female; 257: dorsal; 258: lateral; 259: head, anterior; 260: head, dorsal. Fig. 261: Neotanypeza sp., female, Peru. Fig. 262: Nartshukia musiva Shatalkin (Strongylophthalmyiidae), female holotype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3670837/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3670878>
    dc:description "FIGURES 411–422. Wings: 411: Fergusonina sp. (Fergusoninidae); 412: Odontoloxozus longicornis (Coquillett) (Neriidae); 413: Clisa australis (McAlpine) (Cypselosomatidae); 414: Formicosepsis sp. (Cypselosomatidae); 415: Pseudopomyza (Rhinopomyzella) nigrimana Hennig (Pseudopomyzidae); 416: Latheticomyia sp. (Pseudopomyzidae); 417: Nartshukia musiva Shatalkin, holotype (Strongylophthalmyiidae); 418: Strongylophthalmyia angustipennis Melander (Strongylophthalmyiidae); 419: Tanypeza longimana Fallén (Tanypezidae); 420: Neotanypeza marshalli Lonsdale (Tanypezidae); 421: Compsobata mima (Hennig) (Micropezidae); 422: Micropeza sp. (Micropezidae)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3670878/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3670843>
    dc:description "FIGURES 274–280. Figs 274–278: Strongylophthalmyia angustipennis Melander (Strongylophthalmyiidae), male; 274: dorsal; 275: lateral; 276: head anterior; 277: head, dorsal; 278: head, posterior. Fig. 279: Strongylophthalmyia sp., anteroventral. Fig. 280: Strongylophthalmyia sp., Vietnam." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3670843/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3670847>
    dc:description "FIGURES 286–290. Strongylophthalmyia angustipennis Melander (Strongylophthalmyiidae), female abdomen; 286: ventral; 287: segment 10 and cerci, lateral; 288: same, dorsal; 289: same, ventral; 290: internal genitalia." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3670847/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3670845>
    dc:description "FIGURES 281–285. Strongylophthalmyia angustipennis Melander (Strongylophthalmyiidae), male terminalia; 281: lateral; 282: sternites 6–8, ventral; 283: external genitalia, posterior; 284: internal genitalia (phallus removed), ventral; 285: internal genitalia, left lateral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3670845/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

